      public LeaderCard​(java.lang.String id, Perk assignedPerk, int victoryPoints, java.util.Map<ResourceType,​java.lang.Integer> requiredResources, java.util.Map<CardColor,​java.lang.Integer> requiredDevCards, java.util.Map<CardColor,​CardLevel> requiredDevCardLevel)
      constructor of the Leaader Card at least one between requiredResurces, requiredDevCards and requiredDevCardLevel has to be not null.
      Parameters:
      id - it is the unique id of the card
      assignedPerk - it is the perk of the card
      victoryPoints - are the points gained by activating the card
      requiredResources - are the resources required for activating the card, it can be null
      requiredDevCards - are the DevCardsColors required for activating the card, it can be null
      requiredDevCardLevel - are the DevCardLevels required for activating the card, it can be null
